parameters: Rinny: Hey, can you hear me? I'm your grim reaper.
Rinny: I've slaughtered all your subordinates.
Rinny: I'll gouge out your heart and make you eat it.

Rinny: I'll chase you to the ends of hell and make sure to feed you
your own heart. I am your grim reaper. Enjoy your short life.
Sylvia: Kyle, who was that communication from?

Kyle: Magus General Rinny... he said he's killed all our
subordinates...

Sylvia: Magus General Rinny, huh? He's got good instincts to notice
our relationship.
Kyle: Lady Sylvia... what should I do...

Sylvia: It seems only a matter of time before the Knights of Messiah
start siding with the resistance. That would be troublesome.

Sylvia: Kyle, before the Knights of Messiah arrive, spread poison in
each of the resistance's villages and set them ablaze.

Kyle: Such... You want me to spread poison and burn down the villages
of our own people...?
Kyle: I cannot do it... No matter what Lady Sylvia wishes...
Sylvia: I'll say it again. Do it. It's an order.
Kyle: I can't... I can't do such a thing...
Kyle: Lady Sylvia! Why...!? After all I have done for you...!
Kyle: Why! Why...! Lady Sylvia! Aaahh-...!!

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] A half-baked man whose only merit is betraying his comrades
shouldn't be brandishing his petty justice.
Sylvia: Ahh, my deep kiss went to waste.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Your kisses are too cheap, sister-in-law.
Sylvia: Hehe... I've stolen Rinny's job. I've become his grim reaper.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Also, sister-in-law, there's no need to spread poison or burn
down the villages. It would dirty my country.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Besides, even if the Knights of Messiah join in, nothing will
change.

Sylvia: That's true. If you had said that a bit sooner, this clown
could have been spared from death. Ahahahaha!
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] (In the end, Regnus Grahardt never showed up.)

Sylvia: Hehe... Luuna's power was beyond expectation, but it seems it
wasn't enough to defeat Lord Zena's immortal body.
